snippet.title: Awesomenauts - Starstorm Early Access trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.awesomenauts.com
http://www.facebook.com/Awesomenauts
http://twitter.com/RonimoGames

The successfully Kickstarted Awesomenauts: Starstorm expansion is now available as early access on Steam! Grab it now and receive over a year of updates! Including new characters, a new map, custom game modes, a replay system and a full-fledged spectator mode!

The new Starstorm expansion is available here:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/256500

The Awesomenauts are GO! After conquering the console-battlefields, the Awesomenauts are now taking over the PC! A Mac version will follow soon.

Awesomenauts is out now on Steam! Get the game here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/204300

The game mixes 80's cartoon graphics and platforming gameplay with a deep and modern upgrade system.
